{"tid":1595277,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［新文宣手法］真。文宣郵遞服務","createTime":"2019-09-26T03:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T03:15:15.000Z","uid":64799,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2b4e3aa93efc92d1107d669ca0cea11f8875377d","tid":1595277,"uid":64799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:27:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日落樓收信個時，見到有人鬼鬼祟祟唔知係到做咩。<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：做咩呀你<br />\n佢：派信囉<br />\n我：你又唔係郵差學咩人派信<br />\n佢：唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老細叫我去附近屋苑入傳單宣傳下。話啲呀公呀婆，放工番屋企嘅人都會睇喎<br />\n<br />\n所以呢 我宣布<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">關心香港郵遞服務正式啟動</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">郵差</span></span><br />\n<br />\n準備物資：<br />\n細size 文宣 x適量（postcard 大細或者半張A4左右）<br />\n唔起眼嘅衫褲<br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n1. 去自己座樓樓下or人地屋苑樓下到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 快快手手入啲文宣去郵箱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n(大膽少少嘅可以派曬俾所有人。如果唔係收信個時派少少俾自己郵箱附近嘅都得。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n3. 正正常常咁離開或者番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">注意</span><br />\n。通常屋苑郵箱個邊都有CCTV/藍絲收緊信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 派信個時記得就番角度就ok。見到藍絲可以同佢講派緊傳單。不過最好有法律巴絲講下可能有咩風險。<br />\n<br />\n。如果係自己座樓而且你識啲街坊嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以準備唔同類型文宣俾佢地。 <br />\n例如：<br />\n老人家就簡單易明嘅長輩圖；<br />\n深黃就打氣文宣；<br />\n淺黃就一啲新聞recap、日程表；<br />\n淺藍就警暴圖或者衝擊力大啲嘅文宣；<br />\n深藍就大家自由發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔想做郵差都無問題一樣可以幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">收到文宣嘅街坊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n準備：<br />\n一份心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做法：<br />\n1. 睇下人哋俾你嘅文宣+心意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2. 睇完之後就將張文宣加埋自己嘅心意俾你郵箱附近嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多啲人收到之餘又環保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗等佢哋自己睇新聞/連儂牆就可以update到現況 甚至轉為支持我地。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">928 929 仲有十月一就快到 快啲一齊郵遞啲日程表俾身邊嘅香港人啦</span></span><br />\n覺得有用記得幫手推上熱門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">第一次出post 出錯唔好屌太大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"67ce1a6324e5a709b60d603dbbf6956a0256d126","tid":1595277,"uid":203799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:28:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"44121dd88335567a3498a69ac9577df1aeefb44a","tid":1595277,"uid":64799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:28:51.000Z","msg":"推快啲一齊寄佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"